# Changelog
All notable changes to MokiROV2 will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## ToDo
Fix HOVER PID
Fix PILOT PID
Add Kalman filter for IMU
BUG: Fast switching gamepad directions, crashes rov.js

## [Unreleased]

## [2.0.3] - 2017-10-24
Added Kalman filter for DEPTH
Fixed PONG Timeout

## [2.0.2] - 2017-09-26
Fixed Arduino code, diamond of classes (New class Rov introduced)

## [2.0.1] - 2017-09-12
Fixed PING Timeout (PI -> Arduino)
Added support for 4 lights

## [2.0.0] - 2017-09-12
Major rewrite of the Arduino Code (Now with Classes and C++)
Got rid of the dutch/english mixup of motor and thruster :)
Fixed HOVER PID
Added winston-logstash logging for data analysis
Expanded logfile analysis
Fixed logfile creation fills filesystem to 100%

## [1.0.2] - 2017-09-08
Added version on display
Added update.sh
Added Sensor error on display

## [1.0.1] - 2017-09-06
Added logfile function and analysis.js program (start)
Added IMU Status display (SYSTEM,GYRO,ACCEL,MAG)
Fixed Depth/Pressure int to float (may break hover function)
Fixed PING/PONG ghost echo output
Fixed HUD horizon movement
Fixed IMU Orientation (my setup)
Fixed PILOT PID

## [1.0.0] - 2017-09-06
### Added
- First release :) by @eric.

